EN: At the meeting, the people on the dais were all dressed in formal suits.

ZH: 这个厅里的主席台很宽敞，可以容纳多位领导人。
EN: The podium in this hall is spacious enough to accommodate multiple leaders.

ZH: 他走上主席台，发表了一场朝气蓬勃的演讲。
EN: He stepped onto the rostrum and delivered an energetic speech.

ZH: 主席台上摆放着会议需要的各种文件和纸张。
EN: Various documents and papers needed for the conference were placed on the chairman's podium.

